  "detailed_description": "Finding 21 is a puzzle game that explores the possibility of adding screen lock in a maze game. Gather all the flags in 40+ puzzles!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Screen lock</h2>If you press the space bar, the screen won't move with the character.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/0bd91feac0939a7348dcbdb07e2a589b.poster.avif?t=1621368971\" width=340 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/0bd91feac0939a7348dcbdb07e2a589b.webm?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/0bd91feac0939a7348dcbdb07e2a589b.mp4?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keys and Grey area</h2>When you acquire a key, you gain the ability to erase walls of the same color as the key. When you enter the gray area, the screen fixation function becomes unavailable.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/90f2b1411dbdb1fcf6db6646d057062e.poster.avif?t=1621368971\" width=340 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/90f2b1411dbdb1fcf6db6646d057062e.webm?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/90f2b1411dbdb1fcf6db6646d057062e.mp4?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Finding 21 is a puzzle game that explores the possibility of adding screen lock in a maze game. Gather all the flags in 40+ puzzles!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Screen lock</h2>If you press the space bar, the screen won't move with the character.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/0bd91feac0939a7348dcbdb07e2a589b.poster.avif?t=1621368971\" width=340 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/0bd91feac0939a7348dcbdb07e2a589b.webm?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/0bd91feac0939a7348dcbdb07e2a589b.mp4?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keys and Grey area</h2>When you acquire a key, you gain the ability to erase walls of the same color as the key. When you enter the gray area, the screen fixation function becomes unavailable.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/90f2b1411dbdb1fcf6db6646d057062e.poster.avif?t=1621368971\" width=340 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/90f2b1411dbdb1fcf6db6646d057062e.webm?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357390/extras/90f2b1411dbdb1fcf6db6646d057062e.mp4?t=1621368971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
